  "body": "Currently, the stage4 (transaction replay) calculates receipts to compare their roots with the `receiptHash` in the header, but does not persist it.\r\nWe may want to do it as a separate stage (for the receipts to be retrofitted after the sync is done), or initially just persist them during stage4, and see how much slower it will become as a result.\r\n\r\nBonus: write code for custom RLP serialisation of receipts to reduce GC\r\n\r\nthe option to turn this one is the `r` letter in the `--storage-mode`",
